**Summary**: WA wizard's AI-prefill path (`EnterInfoStep.tsx:175`) uses literal endpoint `'/api/workspace/matters/pre-fill'` — identical to Matter wizard's. T143 fix (commit `3cb239e5d`, applied 2026-06-30) fixed Matter playbook at the Dataverse data layer (DELETE EntityNameValidator orphan + PATCH AI Analysis systemPrompt strip). Because WA dispatches the same endpoint → same consumer-routing row → same playbook, WA inherits the fix by construction. WA's record-copy prefill path (`workAssignmentService.ts:267`) is pure client-side OData via `IDataService` and was never broken by the §10.2/§10.3 root causes.

**Resolution location**: [`notes/audits/wave12-123-three-prefill-wizards.md` §11](../notes/audits/wave12-123-three-prefill-wizards.md)

